<plot>Maggie Cramer lives alone in a backwoods cabin, clinging to the hope that she will once again see her loving husband and avid hunter, Gordon. Years have passed since his mysterious disappearance, but nothing will deter Maggie from keeping the home fires burning. One sultry day, a young stranger (Louis Adams), wounded and wearing a familiar hunting jacket, trespasses on her property. Plagued by suspicion and desperate for the truth, Maggie must decide how far she should push for answers.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?420914</url></doc>
